quotes.quote: It's meaningless to just live, and it's meaningless to just fight. I want to win.

quotes.name: Edward Elric
quotes.quote: A lesson without pain is meaningless. For you cannot gain something without sacrificing something else in return. But once you have recovered it and made it your own... You will gain an irreplaceable Fullmetal heart.

quotes.name: Gildarts Clive
quotes.quote: Fear is not evil. It tells you what weakness is. And once you know your weakness, you can become stronger as well as kinder.

quotes.name: Kenshin Himura
quotes.quote: Whatever you lose, you'll find it again. But what you throw away you'll never get back.
